                        <span class="fw-bold me-2 lh-sm text-dark" style="font-size: 0.95rem;">Autorisé à récupérer l'enfant :</span>
                        <div class="border border-dark border-2 me-1" style="width: 16px; height: 16px; flex-shrink: 0;"></div> <span class="me-2 fw-bold">Oui</span>
                        <div class="border border-dark border-2 me-1" style="width: 16px; height: 16px; flex-shrink: 0;"></div> <span class="fw-bold">Non</span>
                      </h2>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-md-3 mb-3 mb-md-0">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-end">
                      <h2 class="d-flex align-items-end w-100 m-0">
                        <span class="fw-bold fs-5 me-2 text-nowrap text-dark">Profession :</span>
                        <span class="flex-grow-1 border-bottom border-dark border-1" style="height: 24px;">_________________________</span>
